that happened.

133
00:13:11,191 --> 00:13:12,524
Did he do a good job
with the proposal?

134
00:13:12,526 --> 00:13:15,260
Did he do the rose petals?
'Cause that was...

135
00:13:15,262 --> 00:13:17,128
Dude, that's next week.

136
00:13:17,963 --> 00:13:19,430
Um...

137
00:13:20,566 --> 00:13:21,199
