175
00:14:54,293 --> 00:14:55,793
All right.

176
00:14:57,730 --> 00:15:01,232
Well, give us something good!
Kiss her!

177
00:15:04,803 --> 00:15:06,838
Let's see the ring!

178
00:15:08,642 --> 00:15:10,909
