fixer-upper in the country.

204
00:16:15,240 --> 00:16:17,542
- Bravo.
- Hey, hey, hey.

205
00:16:17,544 --> 00:16:20,712
- Is everything okay here?
- Yeah.

206
00:16:21,080 --> 00:16:23,014
Alan was just leaving.

207
00:16:27,186 --> 00:16:28,686
Yeah, so I was.

208
00:16:30,456 --> 00:16:34,792
