what else I can do.

223
00:17:31,884 --> 00:17:34,152
I fucked up. I'm sorry.

224
00:17:34,486 --> 00:17:35,720
And I know it's not an excuse,

225
00:17:35,722 --> 00:17:38,623
but you were completely
wrapped up in work.

226
00:17:42,928 --> 00:17:46,631
